Class Run

java.lang.Object
  org.tuckey.web.filters.urlrewrite.Run

public class Run
extends java.lang.Object

Defines a run element, the ability to run a methodStr (eg, xx(HttpServletRequest httpServletRequest, HttpServletResponse httpServletResponse))
